<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Barcode Scanning API</title>
    <meta property="og:title" content="<%= title %>">
    <meta property="og:description" content="<%= description %>">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://qrcode-rosy-rho.vercel.app/barcode.png"> <!-- Updated image path -->
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://qrcode-rosy-rho.vercel.app/">
    
    <!-- Twitter Card Meta Tags (optional, for Twitter previews) -->
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://qrcode-rosy-rho.vercel.app/barcode.png">
    <style>
        /* Global Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7fb;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #4C6A92;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        pre {
            background-color: #2E3B4E;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }

        code {
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #2E3B4E;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .github-link {
            color: #f4a261;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .github-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            header {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            h3 {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            header {
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }

            h3 {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 0.85rem;
            }

            footer {
                padding: 0.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to the Barcode Scanning API</h1>
        <p>Thank you for visiting! This API allows you to scan barcodes from Base64 encoded images.</p>
        <h2>How to Use the API</h2>
        <p>To use this service, send a POST request to the following endpoint:</p>
        <pre><code>POST https://qrcode-rosy-rho.vercel.app/api/scan</code></pre>
        
        <h3>Request Example</h3>
        <pre><code>
curl -X POST https://qrcode-rosy-rho.vercel.app/api/scan \ 
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{ "imageBase64": "data:image/jpeg;base64,/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQEASABIAAD/..." }'
        </code></pre>
        
        <h3>Response Example</h3>
        <pre><code>
{
    "barcode": "123456789012"
}
        </code></pre>
        
        <p>If you encounter any issues, please check the documentation or contact support.</p>

        <p>Check out the <a href="https://github.com/devjadiya/QRcode/" class="github-link">GitHub repository</a> for more details!</p>
    </header>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Barcode Scanning API</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
